Abu Dhabi PreCast Concrete Plant
Please see Job Details for Apply instructions
Saved!
Job Details
Responsible for controlling and reporting: the company's payroll, the projects accounts (costs, expenses), the company accounts with the suppliers, the suppliers accounts in the company, the customers accounts in the company, the overheads calculations, the profits calculations (gross and net), the cash flow, the company's bank account and the interests, the bank guarantees. Monitoring and reporting the suppliers prices.
Requirements
Accounting Degree 2-5 years experience as a Constructional Contracting Accountant (UAE experience is preferred) Awareness about banks accounting Experience is using MS Office (Excel, Word, Outlook) Ability to enhance the accounting section's procedures Very Good in English talking, listining, reading, writing Arabic language is preferred Driving license is preferred
